Class BetFairCore

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.BetFairCore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    model.IBetFairCore

    public class BetFairCore
extends java.lang.Object
implements model.IBetFairCore
    BetFairCore is a class that implements all the BetFair API methods in the IBetFairCore interface. It is used for all BetFair method calls.

    Craig Thomson
